'''Mugisha Emmanuel''' wamenyekanye nka '''Kibonke Clapton,''' Ni umunya[[rwanda]] wavukiye mu [[Ubugande|bugande]] muri 1988<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/imyidagaduro/sinema/article/igihe-cya-gumamurugo-kibonke-yanditse-filimi-yise-umuturanyi</ref>. yamenyekanye cyane mu kuririmba comedy no gukina filimi zisekeje byatumye ibigo bikomeye byamamaza bimwifashisha nawe bimuha akazi kamuha agatubutse<ref>https://rushyashya.net/mugisha-emmanuel-clapton-uzwi-nka-kibonke-yavuze-ko-ataretse-ibikorwa-byo-gusetsa-ajya-imbere-yabantu-bizwi-nka-standup-comedy-asobanura-ko-kuri-ubu-ahubwo-yahisemo-kuyikora-mu-buryo-bwa-filimi/</ref>. yakinnye muri filimi zakunzwe nka [[SEBURIKOKO]], Agacube, Byadogereye, Virunga high school, Umuturanyi byatumye muri 2017 atangira gutoranywa mubakinnyi 10 bahatanira umukinyi wa filimi w'umwaka.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/201773</ref>

== ubuzima bwa Kibonke  muri make ==
'''Kibonke''' yize amashuri abanza kuri Nyakayaga Primary school, ayisumbuye kuri Kiziguro Secondary School na Kagarama Secondary School nuko Kaminuza ayiga muri University of Kigali (Bacholar of science with honor in science)<ref>http://expressnews.rw/in-profile-clapton-kibonke-rising-christian-comedian-and-singer/</ref>.Kibonke ubu afite umugore barushinze muri 2018 na Mutoni Jacky ubu bafitanye umwana umwe<ref>https://teradignews.rw/clapton-kibonke-yasezeranye-mu-mategeko-numukunzi-we-utwite-amafoto/</ref><ref>https://genesisbizz.com/Ibyishimo-kuri-Kibonke-wavuye-Rwagitima-ubu-akaba-ari-mu-bakinnyi-10-bakunzwe</ref>

== Career ==
Kibonke yatangiye carreer muri 2014 aririmba indirimbo z'Imana  ,muzo yaririmbye harimo" Fata Telephone Mana" " Muri Yesu Harimo gout" , "Ihangane" nizindi<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/85528/kibonke-clapton-yakoze-ubukwe-amafoto-85528.html</ref><sub>,</sub> nyuma muri 2015 yatangiye kwandika no gukina filimi, kuba umushyushyarugamba no kwamamaza<ref>https://www.ktpress.rw/2021/06/comedy-or-nothing-meet-clapton-kibonke/</ref>.<ref>https://igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/umugore-w-umunyarwenya-kibonke-yibarutse-nyuma-y-amezi-hafi-abiri</ref> 

== ibyo utari uzi kuri Kibonke ==
Kibonke akunda abana cyane kandi nabo baramukunda kuko uburyo akina birabashimisha niyompamvu buri mwaka ategura igitaramo cyagenewe gushimisha abana gusa hashize iminsi kitaba kubera covid-19<ref>https://www.thechoicelive.com/mugisha-na-rusine-baje-mukiganiro-basinze-nukireba-uraseka-wihirike-pe-m-irene-yatembagaye</ref><ref>https://touchrwanda.tumblr.com/post/161309760546/kibonke-clapton-yambitse-impeta-umukunzi-we/amp</ref>

